{"tid":1626256,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修 - 兩全其美嘅方法","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T10:53:13.000Z","uid":66895,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2fdab5725c3b971613641b618c217e6cf49e2b23","tid":1626256,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"先講重點：裝修係要做，用一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好睇</span></span>嘅方式，包括用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">水攻</span></span>而非火攻、用遮用得好啲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝修目的係削弱敵人勢力（包括政府、黑警、共產黨、紅色資本、黑色勢力），而我哋另一方面需要鞏固民意支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢一刻民意，比起任何時候更加重要，因為美國正在審議香港民主人權法。如果國際戰線做得好，我哋隨時可以加大制裁力度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。相反，如果做得差，最差情況係有機會令法案無法通過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認同近來嘅裝修行動，因為係削弱敵人勢嘅直接方法。但如果太過暴力，出嚟個畫面唔會好睇，有機會影響民意同國際觀感。所以我有一個兩全其美嘅方法：<br />\n<br />\n1）用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">水攻</span></span>而非火攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。火攻嘅畫面唔好睇，外人睇會覺得好暴力，但係其實造成嘅破壞未必好大。水攻（例如彩彈、噴漆、水泥）可以更有破壞力，出嚟畫面又唔暴力。<br />\n教學：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1330191/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1330191/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n2）遮要更有效咁<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遮鏡頭</span></span>。雖然而家已經會拎遮，但係成日見到大家根本遮唔到個鏡頭。大家想畫面好就遮得好啲。<br />\n<br />\n另外，重申裝修嘅原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n大家可以睇下呢個post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1624486/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1624486/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我覺得應該分得仔細啲<br />\n<br />\n黑裝修 ：福建360，麻雀館，保皇黨，港共政府<br />\n<br />\n紅裝<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">修</span></strong>：中國官方滲透香港嘅國企，如中國銀行、中國移動<br />\n<br />\n中裝<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">飾</span></strong> ：即係油顏色、貼連儂牆紙，雜物塞門口，鎖佢大閘。美心，吉野家，starbuck，三中商等仆街商鋪/中資會降落黎呢個等級。<br />\n<br />\n藍罷買 冇變<br />\n<br />\n黃幫襯 冇變<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1407c9b5a95a5b3db525ab9225dd4835c6989b","tid":1626256,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:24:50.000Z","msg":"認同請推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7383633456e9b92c1a6646a4f080012bd988e3","tid":1626256,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"不完美 可接受 有改善空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe3f62f80539140961434a60d503b1eeef31bb5","tid":1626256,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:27:12.000Z","msg":"兩全其美無理由唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e8e525c6bcd3f64d52877e63e801b984dc0ecc0","tid":1626256,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:28:14.000Z","msg":"光復香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446b400fecf69b49c21db3bc6cf39637e78a498b","tid":1626256,"uid":66895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:28:31.000Z","msg":"時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea2b851f0d8e69f77c7fb541869fb4b6c179d17","tid":1626256,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:32:09.000Z","msg":"裝修完最後搵人是但用D有色既膠條痴幾條<br />\n見到咁都有人去槍  影佢同跟蹤佢"},{"pid":"9bdf22dec48e105f61c7a10111197017feec53d1","tid":1626256,"uid":48119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:40:05.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"543fedd1d2fa03d3e644b5626645f18ecf244a1c","tid":1626256,"uid":257293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:40:34.000Z","msg":"裝修有好多種<br />\n其實裝修可以裝成連儂牆<br />\n